From 0449dac3edcad2ff4c8d6f13e2c92747b9661cdf Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Frogging-Family
From: damachine <damachin3@proton.me>
Date: Fri, 27 Mar 2026 03:13:57 +0100
Subject: [PATCH] Aggressive VM/scheduler/memory tuning defaults

Tuning changes under CONFIG_TKG:
- VM: workingset protection (anon_min, clean_low, clean_min ratios)
- VM: readahead 8M, swap page_cluster=0, vm.swappiness=100
- VM: writeback interval 10s, dirty_background 5%
- VM: disable compaction_proactiveness and watermark_boost_factor
- Scheduler: base_slice 350us, migration_cost 300us, cfs_bandwidth 3ms
- hugepage: defrag kswapd_or_madv, compact_unevictable off under TKG
- init: CONFIG_TKG master toggle + USER_NS_UNPRIVILEGED

Signed-off-by: patch-family-tool <patches@frogging-family.invalid>

